<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <article class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Clash for Windows Resource Hub</p>
      <h1>Clash for Windows 资源中心</h1>
      <p>从安装准备、订阅配置到多设备使用，这里以清晰的步骤和场景化内容帮助你更稳妥地完成客户端设置。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="/dows.html">进入下载中心</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="#latest">查看更新</a>
      </div>
    </article>
    <aside class="hero-panel" aria-label="Clash for Windows 快速入口">
      <img src="https://tse-mm.bing.com/th?q=Clash%20for%20Windows%20dashboard" alt="Clash for Windows 面板界面示意" width="720" height="520" loading="eager">
      <div class="panel-card">
        <span>Windows</span>
        <strong>轻量代理客户端</strong>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="anchor-section">
